OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,FTwo conmen laughed and joked about
OL,7,Fdefrauding elderly people out of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds for roof repairs
OL,9,Fthey did not need.
OL,11,FMaterial recovered from the mobile
OL,12,Fphones of Nelson Cooper and Scott
OL,13,FSmith showed how the pair took great
OL,14,Fpride in preying on vulnerable
OL,15,Fresidents across Kent.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
