CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,FKent Police has released a voice note
OL,7,Fwhere Cooper was singing about
OL,8,F'Christmas money'
OL,10,FThey unscrupulous pair filmed their
OL,11,Fvictims and sent voice notes to each
OL,12,Fother about areas they could target.
OL,14,FCooper stated in one message to a
OL,15,Fcontact that all of the jobs he had
OL,16,Fdone in Ramsgate were over #2,700,
OL,17,Fwhile a second message revealed that
OL,18,Fin Dover 'Ladders are going up left
OL,19,Fright and centre'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
