CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,FHe also sent a voice note singing
OL,7,F'Christmas money' in reference to the
OL,8,Fcash he was making.
OL,10,FKent Police arrested the two in
OL,11,FRamsgate on the 10th January last year
OL,12,Ffollowing reports of cold callers in
OL,13,Fthe area.
OL,15,FSmith was found working on a property
OL,16,Fwhere the elderly resident had already
OL,17,Fpaid more than #25,000 for unnecessary
OL,18,Fwork.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
