FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,FCooper, who had also been there that
OL,7,Fday but fled at the sight of police
OL,8,Fcars, was arrested a short time later.
OL,9,FThey were both charged with a number
OL,10,Fof fraud offences.
OL,12,FAt court they pleaded guilty and on 30
OL,13,FApril 2026 they were both sentenced at
OL,14,FCanterbury Crown Court. Cooper, of
OL,15,FTillingbourne Green in Orpington, was
OL,16,Fgiven a three-year prison sentence and
OL,17,F33 year old Smith of Englefield
OL,18,FCrescent in Orpington was jailed for
OL,19,Ftwo years and four months.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
