OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,FInvestigating officer DC Mark Collins
OL,7,Fsaid, "Our investigation into Cooper
OL,8,Fand Smith's criminal activities was
OL,9,Fable to show how far reaching they had
OL,10,Fbeen and many elderly victims there
OL,11,Fwere, as they destroyed homes with
OL,12,Funnecessary work, took life savings
OL,13,Fand then didn't look back.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,F"When Cooper was arrested and his
OL,7,Fphones were seized, it was distressing
OL,8,Fto see how little respect he had shown
OL,9,Fpeople, from filming them unaware,
OL,10,Feven when they were upset about the
OL,11,Fcostly repairs, to singing and joking
OL,12,Fabout the money he was making from his
OL,13,Ffraud.
OL,15,F"Through determination to uncover the
OL,16,Fevidence needed, officers were able to
OL,17,Fbring them before the courts to stop
OL,18,Fthem taking advantage of any more
OL,19,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
