PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1778623866
OL,3,CRogue roofers laughed and joked about
OL,4,Cconning elderly out of thousands
OL,6,F"Rogue traders like Cooper and Smith
OL,7,Fare often well practiced in their
OL,8,Fscams and the advice they provide can
OL,9,Foften sound very convincing.
OL,11,F"Anyone can become a victim of such
OL,12,Ffrauds so if you are approached out of
OL,13,Fthe blue about repairs needed, don't
OL,14,Fbe rushed into agreeing the work.
OL,15,FDon't be afraid to seek a second
OL,16,Fopinion."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
